The '''Imperial Medallion of Service''' was an award granted by the [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]], to "those who have honored themselves by serving the Empire with excellence and loyalty." [[Lord/Legends|Lord]] [[Hethrir]] granted this award to an Imperial agent who thwarted [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Rebel Alliance]] advances in the [[Corellian system/Legends|Corellian system]].

